# API Design
- Define clear and explicit API endpoints with meaningful names.
- Ensure REST APIs include pagination and filtering to reduce AI processing load.
- Maintain consistent JSON responses for better AI processing.
- Swagger for all API endpoint

# Backend Architecture
- Follow a stateless backend approach to minimize dependency on application state.
- Keep the backend simple and structured to support easy expansion.

